      "text": "Aggressive\nIV hydration\nIf\nfebrile\n, complete cultures and broad spectrum\nantibiotics\nManage Complications\nSee\nDIC\nSee\nLeukostasis\nSee\nHyperviscosity syndrome\nSee\nTumor Lysis Syndrome\nSee\nRetinoic acid syndrome",
